tion costs $200 a month for access to its most sophisticated models. In late May, OpenAI announced a partnership with former Apple $AAPL (AAPL) designer Jony Ive to create 100 million tiny AI devices that CEO Sam Altman believes will somehow change how all consumers interact with technology. He expects them to bring in $1 trillion in revenue. The", "score": 0.75049835, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://pymnts-com-develop.go-vip.net/artificial-intelligence-2/2025/openai-expects-chatgpt-to-have-220-million-paid-subscribers-by-2030", "title": "OpenAI Expects to Have 220 Million Paid Subscribers by 2030", "content": "# OpenAI Expects to Have 220 Million Paid Subscribers by 2030. OpenAI reportedly expects ChatGPT to have at least 220 million paid subscribers by 2030, up from 35 million today. The artificial intelligence (AI) startup also projects that the percentage of weekly users of the AI assistant who become paid subscribers will grow to 8.5% by 2030, up from 5% currently, Reuters reported Wednesday (Nov. 26), citing a paywalled article by The Information. OpenAI expects about 20% of its revenue to come", "score": 0.7265231, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://www.pymnts.com/artificial-intelligence-2/2025/openai-expects-chatgpt-to-have-220-million-paid-subscribers-by-2030", "title": "PYMNTS | OpenAI Expects to Have 220 Million Paid Subscribers by 2030", "content": "OpenAI expects about 20% of its revenue to come from new products related to shopping and advertising, according to the report. For example, the personal shopping assistant for ChatGPT that was released this week could enable monetization through ads or commissions, the report said.", "score": 0.694241, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://techpression.com/openai-extends-deep-research-feature-to-all-paid-chatgpt-subscribers", "title": "OpenAI extends deep research feature to all paid ChatGPT subscribers - Techpression", "content": "their own deep research tools in the same way that OpenAI introdu